						<p>On the south wall, central shrine, Vṛiddhagirīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 9 = 980 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records that Kāḍupaṭṭikaḷ Poṟbhaṭṭaṉ Veṇkāḍaṉ donated ninety sheep for burning a perpetual lamp to Tirumudukuṉṟam-uḍaiyār.</p>						

